thread.title_full: Public Storage reviewed by Ms. Reynolds

author: Ms. Reynolds
title: Ms. Reynolds
text: It is a very clean and trustworthy place. I was a little concerned, however, when I stopped by yesterday and the gate was left opened. I saw a sign that the elevators weren't working, either, so perhaps they were having an issue with electricity. I wish they had a police presence to guard the place while the gates were opened for that amount of time.
